{"tid":1326882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣嘉樂冰室大不如前","createTime":"2019-07-17T11:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T16:00:06.000Z","uid":270282,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46942418e73899e3596973b8dfc9cba3a8e6234c","tid":1326882,"uid":270282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"自轉手後其實有半年冇去食，上網睇轉手後劣評如潮~~<br />\n話哂都食左成十年，有頭髮食到冇頭髮~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前食既係一份老街坊感情~~<br />\n今日一心去懷念下，點知.......<br />\n入面裝修如舊，冇哂大變<br />\n點左個豬排雲吞麵 +凍檸TEA~<br />\n豬排變豬乾~ 茶底明顯差左<br />\n盛惠65~~~多謝都冇句~~食左十年當我欠左家樂~~~~<br />\n有冇BRO SIS 有同感~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dc9b9b0824ead28c156690083d655198c12705","tid":1326882,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e68d30dea1cbe8d6208ce54504df6d0d489c7695","tid":1326882,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"通常轉左手都唔慌好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多嘢留個美好回憶就算 硬係要搞衰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c958d175b65394614bea2612e447757d89831c","tid":1326882,"uid":270282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04dc9b9b0824ead28c156690083d655198c12705","tid":1326882,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecf701a3b0a70dafb161c7c8bce135f5a59bba5","tid":1326882,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2c958d175b65394614bea2612e447757d89831c","tid":1326882,"uid":270282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04dc9b9b0824ead28c156690083d655198c12705","tid":1326882,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:15:31.000Z","msg":"人地拎舊錢去嘆緊世界啦，<br />\n你班傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8918d4a43cea821c32c51190e702171e29f2aa3","tid":1326882,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:47:17.000Z","msg":"嘉樂冰廳 荃灣原址重開！ 五吋超厚蛋牛治經典重現｜小店你好嘢<br />\n<br />\n嘉樂冰廳是荃灣人的集體回憶，以超厚雞蛋三文治而聞名。由1978年開業至今，一直是長龍人氣店，可惜去年宣布退休。在老店面臨結業之際，幸得新老闆接手，且於本月8號已正式重開，新老闆決定保留嘉樂冰廳原貌，並跟舊店師傅學廚數月，務求做回嘉樂冰廳正宗原味！<br />\n<br />\n嘉樂冰廳 荃灣原址重開<br />\n嘉樂冰廳在荃灣已有41年歷史，是區內著名的懷舊冰室，其鮮牛蛋三文治和巨型火腿奄列十分有名，74歲的冰廳老闆麥洪鈞因年事已高，無法再經營生意，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">故今年3月下旬正式對外宣布結業，幸得新買家以3,480萬成交</span></strong>，新買家跟隨麥先生學廚半年時間，務求做到一絲不荀，讓經典得以延續。"},{"pid":"e480084a50171c3071c9d36b4c707c4a9bb332c3","tid":1326882,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"本身都係話好撚好食 抵食就真既<br />\n但排成粒鐘就好撚無謂<br />\n仲有華田沙冰扮奶昔 邊撚到有奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b75df21f47dd5a08f276c27e62786aff6ba795","tid":1326882,"uid":119241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"個炸雲吞難食到好似食緊屎咁"},{"pid":"2bd70d73054bc763e79add62c02c9f2aaa59b969","tid":1326882,"uid":270282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"食緊屎又誇張左。 但又貴又難食係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49da658cdb902bef5ba1d6b04d5e82dc0cf9194","tid":1326882,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"以前都唔係特別好食,賣點只係火腿奄列特別大份"},{"pid":"bb971184586f7e587d02626218ccbd6c65f46c44","tid":1326882,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"屌 根本就唔好食<br />\n係新假期班人吹捧出黎"},{"pid":"07d2171ea9736b68c941208d728bdc5f46a321d4","tid":1326882,"uid":21241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"以前都係得量大"}]}